    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Type of tile used for roofing, usually of fired clay, slate, metal, concrete, asbestos cement, or plastic; available in many configurations and types such as plain tiles, single-lap tiles, and interlocking tiles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000010761/Harris, Dictionary of Architecture and Construction (1975)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Una teja para techos, habitualmente de arcilla cocida, concreto o cemento asbéstico, disponible en muchas configuraciones y tipos, tales como tejas planas, tejas para traslape único y tejas ensambladas. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Een tegel voor dakbedekking die meestal is gemaakt van gebakken klei, beton of asbestcement en verkrijgbaar is in vele samenstellingen en soorten zoals platte dakpannen, enkelsnedige dakpannen en tegels die in elkaar grijpen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000052426/Vakwoordenboek Bouw (1995)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tipo de telha usada para cobertura, geralmente de barro cozido, ardósia, metal, concreto, fibrocimento ou plástico; disponível em muitas configurações e tipos, como telhas simples, telhas de volta única e telhas intertravadas.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000316/CVAA-BR</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
